    {{#IstEnglisch}}
    <div id="englisch">
        <p>
            Hello
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for your interest in documents from the Federal Archives.
        </p>

        <p>
            As you can see from the order overview in your <a href="https://www.recherche.bar.admin.ch/recherche/#/en/account/orders">user account</a>, we prepared some documents for you to consult in the reading room on {{Lesesaaltermin}}.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you wish to consult the documents within the next five working days, please let us know when you would like to do so. Unless we hear from you within 48 hours, or if you are unable to consult the documents within the next five days, we will put them back into storage.
        </p>

        <p>
            Thank you for your understanding. Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions.
        </p>

        <p>
            Yours sincerely
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>{{User.Vorname}} {{User.Name}}</b>
        </p>
